Package: ferxtranslate
Title: Translate Pharmacometric Models to ferx Format
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Teun", "Post", email = "teunpost@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Translates pharmacometric models written in NONMEM, nlmixr2, or
    Monolix into ferx .ferx format. Uses nonmem2rx and rxode2 as parsing
    intermediaries so that a single adapter covers all three source formats.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    cli,
    nonmem2rx,
    rxode2
Suggests:
    knitr,
    monolix2rx,
    rmarkdown,
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
